WEBVTT

NOTE Festival Cut narration captions. Hand-aligned to the 269.9-second
NOTE gpt-audio onyx render. Paragraph boundaries match the SSML script.
NOTE Timing is approximate (within ±2 seconds). Re-time via WhisperX
